Date of Birth: May 9, 1796<br/>
Birthplace: Fairfield, New York, USA<br/>
Ordained apostle: April 8, 1841<br/>
Excommunicated: December 3, 1848<br/>
Death: March 31, 1858<br/>
<br/>
Born May 9, 1796, at Fairfield, Herkimer Co., New York, to Levi Wight and Sarah Corbin.
Ordained apostle April 8, 1841, by Joseph Smith, at Nauvoo, Illinois, at age 44;
excommunicated Dec. 3, 1848; died March 31, 1858, in Dexter, Texas, at age 63.